wikipedia_page.main: Daniel O'Callaghan was an Irish Labour Party politician. He was elected as a Labour Party Teachta Dála (TD) to the 3rd Dáil at the 1922 general election for the Wexford constituency. He lost his seat at the 1923 general election.
